足，boxing可補全之。</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n利申唔識, 呢句野錯係邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n泰拳係拳、腳、膝、肘四方面都會重視，拳頭攻擊不足係你自己技術問題</blockquote><br />\n四方面都重視，係理論層面的片面之辭。<br />\n<br />\n泰拳的腳、膝、肘已包含左短、中、長的強力打擊，<br />\n<br />\n而拳卻只係中距離，加上泰拳的拳動作太大，實戰時，容易被腳反攻，故不被重視，Boxing 正可補全呢一點。<br />\n<br />\n（唔信喞，可以youtube看下Tony Jaa同第二啲泰拳手點打。）"},{"pid":"e6156d341266683cf13456ae1712c4e052af14f8","tid":105252,"uid":27163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T13:52:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n利申唔識, 呢句野錯係邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n泰拳係拳、腳、膝、肘四方面都會重視，拳頭攻擊不足係你自己技術問題</blockquote><br />\n四方面都重視，係理論層面的片面之辭。<br />\n<br />\n泰拳的腳、膝、肘已包含左短、中、長的強力打擊，<br />\n<br />\n而拳卻只係中距離，加上泰拳的拳動作太大，實戰時，容易被腳反攻，故不被重視，Boxing 正可補全呢一點。<br />\n<br />\n（唔信喞，可以youtube看下Tony Jaa同第二啲泰拳手點打。）</blockquote><br />\n播求係k1屌打kick boxing世界級高手又點計？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92c0d00a55ed89a85c992d008f48a40afe6f15a6","tid":105252,"uid":27163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T13:55:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n利申唔識, 呢句野錯係邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n泰拳係拳、腳、膝、肘四方面都會重視，拳頭攻擊不足係你自己技術問題</blockquote><br />\n四方面都重視，係理論層面的片面之辭。<br />\n<br />\n泰拳的腳、膝、肘已包含左短、中、長的強力打擊，<br />\n<br />\n而拳卻只係中距離，加上泰拳的拳動作太大，實戰時，容易被腳反攻，故不被重視，Boxing 正可補全呢一點。<br />\n<br />\n（唔信喞，可以youtube看下Tony Jaa同第二啲泰拳手點打。）</blockquote><br />\n我知道係片面之詞，但係個個師父教野都有唔同，唔係個個都會重肘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"122cdc206a8501225fbed7a39f6cb9a652fb56d0","tid":105252,"uid":27163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T13:57:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n利申唔識, 呢句野錯係邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n泰拳係拳、腳、膝、肘四方面都會重視，拳頭攻擊不足係你自己技術問題</blockquote><br />\n四方面都重視，係理論層面的片面之辭。<br />\n<br />\n泰拳的腳、膝、肘已包含左短、中、長的強力打擊，<br />\n<br />\n而拳卻只係中距離，加上泰拳的拳動作太大，實戰時，容易被腳反攻，故不被重視，Boxing 正可補全呢一點。<br />\n<br />\n（唔信喞，可以youtube看下Tony Jaa同第二啲泰拳手點打。）</blockquote><br />\n如果泰拳都動作大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁跆拳道咪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86d4e9980443119d1a82cf225d46118acad589e1","tid":105252,"uid":2033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T14:03:29.000Z","msg":"無問題 反正樓豬都係做沙包<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b1f2597c8f725edd952f3fe9849cd942adc9d74","tid":105252,"uid":5523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T14:04:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>泰拳不重拳頭而重肘，故拳頭攻擊不足，boxing可補全之。</blockquote><br />\n<img s